indexing.utils

Class KnnSearchResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • indexing.utils.KnnSearchResults
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SearchResults

    public class KnnSearchResults
extends java.lang.Object
implements SearchResults
    Data structure to store matches of a knn-search. New Matches are added only if they are closer to the query than existing matches (the furtherst match is therefore removed) or if there are less than k matches in the structure.
    Author:
    Pierre Tirilly - pierre.tirilly@imt-lille-douai.fr
